Jordanie?

02:03:38.828 --> 02:03:41.496
Putain de Jésus Christ !

02:03:41.497 --> 02:03:43.081
Qu'as-tu pris ?

02:03:43.082 --> 02:03:44.458
Qu'est-ce qui ne va pas?

02:03:44.459 --> 02:03:45.542
Jor!

02:03:45.543 --> 02:03:48.003
